 — Meeting123\nMeeting123 — discussed — SupplyChainRisk\nSupplyChainRisk — affects — Q3Planning\nVendorContracts — requireFollowUpBy — User\n```\n\nSo:\n\n- **PKM**: flexible, personal, note-centered, human-readable.\n- **Knowledge graph / EGGF-like system**: structured, relational, machine-readable, often designed for retrieval, reasoning, or automation.\n\nIn short, a PKM system can contain graph-like links, but it is usually not the same as a formal knowledge graph framework. A PKM is for **personal sensemaking**; an EGGF, if graph-based, would be more about **structured knowledge representation and use by systems or AI**.",
